<A HREF="main.phtml#1.0 Poll"><B>Polls:</B></A><BR>
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="ARIEL">
Here are the results from the last poll. The question was <I>"Which of the following common complaints about Kunark would you most like to see addressed?"</I></FONT><BR><BR>

<FONT SIZE="1" FACE="ARIEL">
1. More spell drops   17.03% (62 votes)<BR>
2. More loot   23.63% (86 votes)<BR>
3. More experience   21.43% (78 votes)<BR>
4. Better framerates   23.35% (85 votes)<BR>
5. Less bugs   14.56% (53 votes)<BR>
<B>-------------------</B><BR>
<B>Total Votes:</B> 364</FONT><BR><BR>

<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="ARIEL">
All the complaints pretty much share equal preference among the voters, with #4 Better Framerates and #2 More Loot being almost dead even. Hopefully, with Velious, Verant will not make the same mistakes and we won't need a 1 GHZ machine to play the new zones *grin*.<BR><BR>

In light of the big announcement about the upcoming expansion pack, this weeks new poll will ask <I>"Do you intend to purchase the expansion pack "The Scars of Velious" when it is released?"</I>.</FONT><BR><BR>

